data.title: Compelled Original Quad Movie Poster (1960) Starring Ronald Howard & Beth Rogan by Ramsey Harrington: Good Poster (1960)
data.meta_description: Poster - United Artists, United Kingdom - 1960 - Condition: Good - 30 by 40 cms approx. Vertical centrefold marks. Some light nicks, creases & stains to edges of front of poster. Some light stains to fold marks on rear. Biro writing on rear. Else good. - Compelled Original Quad Movie Poster (1960) Starring Ronald Howard & Beth Rogan
